        How-It-Works section's texture language. */}
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.025] pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(45,200,86,1) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;" aria-hidden="true"></div>
