          <div class="h-px w-8 bg-evium-green"></div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        {[
          {
            q: "How do I join the Evium partner network?",
            a: "Click the 'Apply to Partner With Us' button on this page and fill out the partner application. We'll review your credentials and reach out within a few business days to schedule an introductory call. If there's a fit, we'll add you to our active partner list for your region.",
          },
          {
            q: "What licenses or certifications do I need?",
            a: "At minimum, you need to be a state-licensed electrical contractor (or hold a master electrician license) in the state where you want to perform installations. If you operate across state lines, we'll need credentials for each relevant jurisdiction. OSHA 10/30 and NEC familiarity are expected.",
          },
          {
            q: "Who supplies the equipment?",
            a: "Evium handles all equipment procurement and coordinates delivery to the job site before your mobilization date. You do not source, purchase, or own the hardware — your scope is purely labor and installation.",
          },
          {
            q: "How is payment structured?",
            a: "Payment is milestone-based, tied to key installation phases (typically: mobilization, rough-in completion, and commissioning sign-off). Payment terms are outlined in the subcontractor agreement before any project begins. We do not run net-60 or net-90 cycles — electricians who deliver get paid promptly.",
          },
          {
            q: "Do you provide EV charger installation training?",
            a: "Yes. Evium provides installation specification packages, pre-project briefings, and access to manufacturer documentation for every project. If you have strong commercial electrical fundamentals but limited EV charging experience, we'll bring you up to speed before your first project.",
          },
          {
            q: "How much work can I realistically expect?",
            a: "That depends on your geography, crew size, and performance. Some partners work on one or two Evium projects a month; others — especially those in our fastest-growing markets — are engaged much more frequently. High-performing partners receive early pipeline access and are prioritized for larger, multi-stall deployments.",
          },
        ].map((faq) => (
          <details class="group bg-evium-dark border border-white/[0.08] rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors duration-200">
              <span class="text-white font-semibold text-sm leading-relaxed">{faq.q}</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"/></svg>
            </summary>
